# Card Styling Standards

When creating card components in this project, use these compact styles:

## Card Container
- **Width**: `max-w-[16rem]` (compact)
- **Padding**: `px-3 py-2` (reduced vertical padding)
- **Border**: `rounded-xl border bg-card`
- **Spacing**: `space-y-2` for internal sections

## Example

```jsx
<div className="max-w-[16rem]">
  <div className="rounded-xl border bg-card px-3 py-2 space-y-2">
    {/* Card content */}
  </div>
</div>
```

## Guidelines
- Keep cards compact with minimal padding
- Use `space-y-2` for tight vertical rhythm
- Prefer `text-sm` for card content
- Use `text-muted-foreground` for labels
